### Implementation Notes

#### Horizontal Wave Implementation
Use `data-col` and `data-row` attributes on cards (build-time generated):
```html
<div class="card" data-col="0" data-row="0">Card 1</div>
<div class="card" data-col="1" data-row="0">Card 2</div>
<div class="card" data-col="2" data-row="0">Card 3</div>
```

Stagger calculation: `delay = (column_index Ã— 150ms) + (row_index Ã— 50ms)`

#### Mobile Optimization
- Threshold: 0.05 (mobile users scroll faster)
- RootMargin: `0px 0px -10% 0px` (triggers earlier)
- Disable lateral (X-axis) movement if element width > 90% viewport

#### Reduced Motion Support
Always respect `prefers-reduced-motion`:
```css
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  /* Disable or simplify animations */
}
```

